Package co.acoustic.mobile.push.sdk.api

Interface SdkInitLifecycleCallbacks

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MceApplication
    public interface SdkInitLifecycleCallbacks
    This interface is for receiving callbacks during the different stages of the sdk init process.
